text: Ștefan Musei (born 10 December 1995) is a Romanian luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Romania Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
